examples.text: The purpose of this program is to reduce 75% of the cancer incidence resulting from area sources (defined as stationary sources which emit less than 10 tons of a single HAP or 25 tons of a combination of HAPs) of hazardous air pollutants in urban areas.

glosses: A person's lot (good or bad), luck, fortune, fate.
A stroke of good or bad luck, an occurrence or happening, especially an unexpected, random, chance, or fortuitous event.

examples.text: Cursed be good haps, and cursed be they that build / Their hopes on haps, and do not make despair / For all these certain blows the surest shield.
